The 2022 Webby nominees represent the most innovative and creative work on the internet — from immersive and virtual world experiences like Gucci Garden Archetypes, Sneaker 0, and Lonely Echo II, to high-quality storytelling in projects like Amazon Music’s The Walk In, MoMA Photo Club, Better | Mamba Forever, A Mars Rover Looks Back, and boundary-pushing games like The Artful Escape by Annapurna Interactive, Hoa by PM Studios inc., to podcasts like Smartless, Scam Goddess, Blindspot: Tulsa Burning, and Storytime with Seth Rogan.All winners will be celebrated during a star-studded, in-person show for the 26th Annual Webby Awards on 16 May 2022.Nominees are also competing to win The Webby People’s Voice Awards. Voting is open for the public and closes on 21 April 2022.For more, go to vote.webbyawards.com